<br>
Let me put this into words you can understand.<br>
<br>
1 group of 6 level 65's as it stands now makes 1.44% AA on every single kill.  (on level 63 creatures, like you would be killing in, say, Valor).<br>
<br>
After the change, this SAME group killing the SAME mobs, will earn 1.78% AA on every kill.<br>
<br>
Wow, an additional .24 percent!  I know I'm excited to be going from 69 kills per AA to 56 kills per AA, thats like 15 minutes per AA!  [going from 1 hour 30 minutes to 1 hour 15 minutes]<br>
<br>
This isn't a group bonus, its a solo nerf.<br>
<br>
Look at the solo aspect:<br>
Currently it takes approximately 14 kills if you are kiting in Valor. I'm going to estimate this as 50 minutes per AA for those who can accomplish it. <br>
You are earning 7.18% AA per mob.<br>
<br>
After the change you will be earning 4.95% AA per mob. This means you will need 20 mobs (well, you will have to kill .2% of another, but whatever).<br>
<br>
This puts you at 1 hour and 20 minutes per AA.<br>
In theory, this works well--except you still have to spend 10+ minutes each time getting buffed (C3, SoE, whatever).<br>
<br>
I worked out the math for everyone.  If the ZEM is lowered only to 120 (a number I suggested earlier because it means that groups larger than 2 will gain a benefit, while groups less than 2 will see a negative impact) you will see this:<br>
Solo: 1 Hour. (Normally a little slower than this)<br>
Group: 1 Hour. (Normally a litle faster than this)<br>
<br>
This is using parsed times.  Sorry, my parsed times for wizards was relatively limited, as I don't solo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dalrenfieryblade>Dalren Fieryblade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 208<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/03 11:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: erm</span><hr size=1> I have to agree with this, grouping exp SHOULD be better, this is an mmorpg, you are meant to group.<br>
